Delete this entire band band please when you're finished. Issue # 287
1.) write a data source to match the labels presented. 2.) chart controls are asking for the minimum of the score in the scorecard name stated. 3.) You'll have to make groups for these items based on the data source you create. Groups should ultimately reflect: 1 BA has many BPs. No BA cards on this report. 1 BP has many CARDS for the cards. 1 BP has many milestones and each has a response. 4.) Barbara wants parameters to show up user selectable. Show / hide information. Just like in old readycert. Filter by name. Show Description. Show BA scorecard. Show IA scorecard. Show TA scorecard. Show BCM. Show library attachment. 5.) lastly keep in mind that this is an agnostic report for assessment, and its a big one so let's find the solution that doesn't require sorting by specific card names. 6.) This is 1 report at the project level. This report should be duplicated for enterprise and the user allowed to select a project (I would only run 1 project on this report, the point of it being in enterprise is the user may report on other projects regardless of what project they're in. Barbara might wish to select multi value here, ask her about that). 7.) goes without saying but delete the devhelp red boxes
